  "corner_label": "Screen English",
  "title": "",
  "movie": "애프터 웨딩 인 뉴욕 (After the Wedding)",
  "duration_sec": 663.43,
  "audio_url": "https://pub-7f9ded590f88439d8f48752f6639e723.r2.dev/2021-10-20_screen_english.mp3",
  "artwork_generated_url": "",
  "script": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 1.56,
      "text": "크리스쌤 하이"
    },
    {
      "start": 1.56,
      "end": 2.4,
      "text": "우승우승"
    },
    {
      "start": 2.4,
      "end": 3.28,
      "text": "Hello"
    },
    {
      "start": 3.28,
      "end": 6.08,
      "text": "네 이렇게 기쁘게 인사 건네주셨고요."
    },
    {
      "start": 6.92,
      "end": 12.18,
      "text": "이 After Wedding in New York 이라는 제목 하에 우리가 내용을 살펴보고 있잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 12.44,
      "end": 14.14,
      "text": "Yeah things are getting really really serious."
    },
    {
      "start": 14.36,
      "end": 19.5,
      "text": "어 근데 일단 Wedding in New York 이거 자체만 한번 상상을 해보면"
    },
    {
      "start": 19.5,
      "end": 20.92,
      "text": "That sounds like a good event."
    },
    {
      "start": 20.98,
      "end": 23.52,
      "text": "Yeah 아주 로맨틱하고 wonderful 할 것 같습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 23.76,
      "end": 24.6,
      "text": "It's an outdoor wedding"
    },
    {
      "start": 24.6,
      "end": 25.3,
      "text": "Oh 맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 25.48,
      "end": 28.2,
      "text": "At a private home in the front yard"
    },
    {
      "start": 28.2,
      "end": 31.36,
      "text": "네 저의 상상을 좀 더 구체화 시켜주시니까 너무 행복해지네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 31.42,
      "end": 32.26,
      "text": "Beautiful flowers"
    },
    {
      "start": 32.26,
      "end": 32.7,
      "text": "Wow"
    },
    {
      "start": 32.7,
      "end": 34.2,
      "text": "Beautiful green lawn"
    },
    {
      "start": 34.2,
      "end": 35.4,
      "text": "와 너무 아름다워요."
    },
    {
      "start": 35.6,
      "end": 36.72,
      "text": "Close friends and family"
    },
    {
      "start": 36.72,
      "end": 39.16,
      "text": "네 아마 그렇게 이 테레사도"
    },
    {
      "start": 39.16,
      "end": 41.08,
      "text": "Had a wedding in New York 했었을 겁니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 41.62,
      "end": 42.08,
      "text": "She did"
    },
    {
      "start": 42.08,
      "end": 42.56,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 42.56,
      "end": 44.64,
      "text": "근데 만약에 이제"
    },
    {
      "start": 44.64,
      "end": 49.2,
      "text": "Would have been so nice if the marriage was continuously romantic forever"
    },
    {
      "start": 49.2,
      "end": 51.44,
      "text": "Oh wouldn't that be nice?"
    },
    {
      "start": 51.58,
      "end": 53.84,
      "text": "Wouldn't it be nice for everybody"
    },
    {
      "start": 53.84,
      "end": 55.8,
      "text": "If the romance lasted"
    },
    {
      "start": 55.8,
      "end": 56.3,
      "text": "Uh-huh"
    },
    {
      "start": 56.3,
      "end": 58.34,
      "text": "하지만 그렇게 되기가 좀 쉽지는 않죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 58.46,
      "end": 58.72,
      "text": "그쵸?"
    },
    {
      "start": 58.92,
      "end": 59.28,
      "text": "Sure"
    },
    {
      "start": 59.28,
      "end": 60.06,
      "text": "Hamilton"
    },
    {
      "start": 60.06,
      "end": 63.52,
      "text": "Now we happen to focus on the story about Teresa"
    },
    {
      "start": 63.52,
      "end": 64.82,
      "text": "Yeah Teresa"
    },
    {
      "start": 64.82,
      "end": 66.44,
      "text": "So she was"
    },
    {
      "start": 66.44,
      "end": 67.76,
      "text": "This is kind of a spoiler"
    },
    {
      "start": 67.76,
      "end": 69.4,
      "text": "But we mentioned it yesterday"
    },
    {
      "start": 69.4,
      "end": 69.96,
      "text": "Wow"
    },
    {
      "start": 69.96,
      "end": 70.98,
      "text": "This is the time"
    },
    {
      "start": 70.98,
      "end": 72.46,
      "text": "This is another big twist"
    },
    {
      "start": 72.46,
      "end": 73.82,
      "text": "The time is to reveal"
    },
    {
      "start": 73.82,
      "end": 74.42,
      "text": "Here is here"
    },
    {
      "start": 74.42,
      "end": 74.62,
      "text": "Okay"
    },
    {
      "start": 74.62,
      "end": 76.42,
      "text": "To reveal another big twist"
    },
    {
      "start": 76.42,
      "end": 76.74,
      "text": "Uh-huh"
    },
    {
      "start": 76.74,
      "end": 79.3,
      "text": "So she has an illness"
    },
    {
      "start": 79.3,
      "end": 81.54,
      "text": "Not a light illness"
    },
    {
      "start": 81.54,
      "end": 83.04,
      "text": "It's a terminal illness"
    },
    {
      "start": 83.04,
      "end": 85.44,
      "text": "Oh you mean incurable disease"
    },
    {
      "start": 85.44,
      "end": 86.08,
      "text": "Incurable"
    },
    {
      "start": 86.08,
      "end": 86.56,
      "text": "Oh"
    },
    {
      "start": 86.56,
      "end": 89.34,
      "text": "So she doesn't have much longer to live"
    },
    {
      "start": 89.34,
      "end": 89.88,
      "text": "Uh-oh"
    },
    {
      "start": 89.88,
      "end": 90.72,
      "text": "Terminally ill"
    },
    {
      "start": 90.72,
      "end": 93.48,
      "text": "And she has been hiding this from all her family"
    },
    {
      "start": 93.48,
      "end": 94.08,
      "text": "So sad"
    },
    {
      "start": 94.08,
      "end": 95.02,
      "text": "Nobody knows"
    },
    {
      "start": 95.02,
      "end": 97.86,
      "text": "She doesn't want to trouble them with her illness"
    },
    {
      "start": 97.86,
      "end": 99.72,
      "text": "She hides her medicine"
    },
    {
      "start": 99.72,
      "end": 100.5,
      "text": "Uh-huh"
    },
    {
      "start": 100.5,
      "end": 101.68,
      "text": "And she locks it away"
    },
    {
      "start": 101.68,
      "end": 102.1,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 102.1,
      "end": 103.52,
      "text": "It felt for her so much"
    },
    {
      "start": 103.52,
      "end": 103.9,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 103.9,
      "end": 105.42,
      "text": "So when we find this out"
    },
    {
      "start": 105.42,
      "end": 106.58,
      "text": "We do feel for her"
    },
    {
      "start": 106.58,
      "end": 108.44,
      "text": "We understand her situation"
    },
    {
      "start": 108.44,
      "end": 112.22,
      "text": "And why she is doing all these seemingly crazy things"
    },
    {
      "start": 112.22,
      "end": 113.32,
      "text": "She has a reason"
    },
    {
      "start": 113.32,
      "end": 113.74,
      "text": "네"
    },
    {
      "start": 113.74,
      "end": 116.96,
      "text": "치료할 수 없는 불치병으로 인해서"
    },
    {
      "start": 116.96,
      "end": 120.38,
      "text": "정말 시안부 선고를 받은 상황이었다라는 거죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 120.38,
      "end": 123.82,
      "text": "그래서 이제 얼마 남지 않은 삶을 두고"
    },
    {
      "start": 123.82,
      "end": 125.42,
      "text": "정리도 하고"
    },
    {
      "start": 125.42,
      "end": 129.8,
      "text": "그러면서 이제 이자벨을 찾은 이유가 다 있었다라는 걸 이해하게 됩니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 129.8,
      "end": 131.58,
      "text": "그나저나 정말"
    },
    {
      "start": 131.58,
      "end": 134.04,
      "text": "I can't imagine how hard it is"
    },
    {
      "start": 134.04,
      "end": 134.62,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 134.62,
      "end": 137.82,
      "text": "나의 입장이라면 얼마나 이게 힘들까"
    },
    {
      "start": 137.82,
      "end": 138.44,
      "text": "If it were you"
    },
    {
      "start": 138.44,
      "end": 140.36,
      "text": "상상도 못하겠어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 140.36,
      "end": 142.54,
      "text": "She has to call her daughters"
    },
    {
      "start": 142.54,
      "end": 144.86,
      "text": "The girl she raised as a daughter"
    },
    {
      "start": 144.86,
      "end": 147.44,
      "text": "Call her real mom from India"
    },
    {
      "start": 147.44,
      "end": 149.16,
      "text": "Give her money"
    },
    {
      "start": 149.16,
      "end": 150.24,
      "text": "Okay"
    },
    {
      "start": 150.24,
      "end": 153.62,
      "text": "Now we understand why she wants her to stay in New York"
    },
    {
      "start": 153.62,
      "end": 156.84,
      "text": "I think she's trying to arrange all her affairs"
    },
    {
      "start": 156.84,
      "end": 159.46,
      "text": "For after she passes away"
    },
    {
      "start": 159.46,
      "end": 164.44,
      "text": "음 사실 뭐 누군가에게 가족까지 포함해가지고"
    },
    {
      "start": 164.44,
      "end": 167.44,
      "text": "Give everything 한다라는 거 쉽지 않은 일이잖아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 167.44,
      "end": 167.86,
      "text": "Sure"
    },
    {
      "start": 167.86,
      "end": 169.95,
      "text": "와 참 공감이 많이 됩니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 169.95,
      "end": 173.27,
      "text": "일단은 오늘 장면 먼저 듣고 오겠습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 173.27,
      "end": 175.41,
      "text": "I hate fighting with you"
    },
    {
      "start": 175.41,
      "end": 178.09,
      "text": "You think you're ever going to forgive me?"
    },
    {
      "start": 178.99,
      "end": 180.01,
      "text": "That's my other option"
    },
    {
      "start": 180.01,
      "end": 181.91,
      "text": "But I want to know everything"
    },
    {
      "start": 181.91,
      "end": 184.56,
      "text": "When you give a child up for adoption"
    },
    {
      "start": 184.56,
      "end": 186.96,
      "text": "You've got 30 days to change your mind"
    },
    {
      "start": 186.96,
      "end": 189.04,
      "text": "A grace period"
    },
    {
      "start": 189.04,
      "end": 192.06,
      "text": "How long did it take you to decide to come get me?"
    },
    {
      "start": 192.58,
      "end": 193.38,
      "text": "29 days"
    },
    {
      "start": 193.38,
      "end": 195.52,
      "text": "Actually"
    },
    {
      "start": 195.52,
      "end": 197.26,
      "text": "이 장면을 들으면서"
    },
    {
      "start": 197.26,
      "end": 198.58,
      "text": "I thought of a saying that"
    },
    {
      "start": 198.58,
      "end": 201.28,
      "text": "Blood is thicker than water"
    },
    {
      "start": 201.28,
      "end": 202.28,
      "text": "That's a good saying"
    },
    {
      "start": 202.28,
      "end": 205.34,
      "text": "피는 물보다 진하다라는 말이 생각이 났어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 205.34,
      "end": 206.9,
      "text": "Blood is thicker than water"
    },
    {
      "start": 206.9,
      "end": 207.32,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 207.32,
      "end": 207.92,
      "text": "왜냐하면"
    },
    {
      "start": 207.92,
      "end": 209.96,
      "text": "She was so angry a lot"
    },
    {
      "start": 209.96,
      "end": 210.46,
      "text": "그죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 210.62,
      "end": 211.06,
      "text": "Furious"
    },
    {
      "start": 211.06,
      "end": 212.6,
      "text": "왜냐하면 아빠한테 약간"
    },
    {
      "start": 212.6,
      "end": 215.58,
      "text": "Betrayed 당했다라고 생각을 했었을 테니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 215.58,
      "end": 217.22,
      "text": "화가 많이 났었을 거란 말이죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 217.22,
      "end": 218.96,
      "text": "I would be angry at first too"
    },
    {
      "start": 218.96,
      "end": 220.42,
      "text": "Her dad told her"
    },
    {
      "start": 220.42,
      "end": 221.52,
      "text": "Her mom died"
    },
    {
      "start": 221.52,
      "end": 223.32,
      "text": "While her mom is alive"
    },
    {
      "start": 223.32,
      "end": 224.18,
      "text": "She's healthy"
    },
    {
      "start": 224.18,
      "end": 225.44,
      "text": "She's living in India"
    },
    {
      "start": 225.44,
      "end": 227.66,
      "text": "But he didn't say anything about them"
    },
    {
      "start": 227.66,
      "end": 229.84,
      "text": "그래서 엄청 화가 나서"
    },
    {
      "start": 229.84,
      "end": 233.38,
      "text": "다시는 용서하지 않을 것 같아 보였지만"
    },
    {
      "start": 233.38,
      "end": 234.72,
      "text": "그리고 나서"
    },
    {
      "start": 234.72,
      "end": 238.26,
      "text": "She didn't try to make up with him again"
    },
    {
      "start": 238.26,
      "end": 238.66,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 238.66,
      "end": 240.14,
      "text": "So she realizes"
    },
    {
      "start": 240.14,
      "end": 241.5,
      "text": "This is her dad"
    },
    {
      "start": 241.5,
      "end": 243.06,
      "text": "No matter what he did"
    },
    {
      "start": 243.06,
      "end": 244.22,
      "text": "She loves her dad"
    },
    {
      "start": 244.22,
      "end": 246.22,
      "text": "And she wants to be close to him"
    },
    {
      "start": 246.22,
      "end": 247.86,
      "text": "So she has no choice"
    },
    {
      "start": 247.86,
      "end": 249.62,
      "text": "But to forgive him"
    },
    {
      "start": 249.62,
      "end": 250.94,
      "text": "And I also understand"
    },
    {
      "start": 250.94,
      "end": 252.52,
      "text": "He wanted to protect his daughter"
    },
    {
      "start": 252.52,
      "end": 253.22,
      "text": "That's right"
    },
    {
      "start": 253.22,
      "end": 255.32,
      "text": "Because he was afraid she would be hurt"
    },
    {
      "start": 255.32,
      "end": 258.22,
      "text": "If she found out that her mom just left"
    },
    {
      "start": 258.22,
      "end": 260.04,
      "text": "And gave her up for adoption"
    },
    {
      "start": 260.04,
      "end": 262.44,
      "text": "But I don't know"
    },
    {
      "start": 262.44,
      "end": 264.82,
      "text": "When should he tell her"
    },
    {
      "start": 264.82,
      "end": 266.72,
      "text": "That her mom is alive?"
    },
    {
      "start": 267.58,
      "end": 269.2,
      "text": "처음부터 죽었던 얘기"
    },
    {
      "start": 269.2,
      "end": 270.36,
      "text": "안 했으면 되는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 270.36,
      "end": 270.74,
      "text": "맞아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 270.74,
      "end": 271.72,
      "text": "아무튼"
    },
    {
      "start": 271.72,
      "end": 273.96,
      "text": "자 주요 표현들 점검을 해볼까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 274.54,
      "end": 275.38,
      "text": "Other option"
    },
    {
      "start": 275.38,
      "end": 276.68,
      "text": "Other option"
    },
    {
      "start": 276.68,
      "end": 278.12,
      "text": "다른 선택지"
    },
    {
      "start": 278.12,
      "end": 279.52,
      "text": "혹은 다른 방법"
    },
    {
      "start": 279.52,
      "end": 281.02,
      "text": "이라고 해석하시면 됐네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 281.02,
      "end": 282.6,
      "text": "We have no other option"
    },
    {
      "start": 282.6,
      "end": 284.96,
      "text": "Or what is the other option?"
    },
    {
      "start": 285.32,
      "end": 287.2,
      "text": "다른 선택지가 뭐가 있을까?"
    },
    {
      "start": 287.64,
      "end": 289.06,
      "text": "다른 방법은 없을까?"
    },
    {
      "start": 289.26,
      "end": 289.88,
      "text": "라고 할 때"
    },
    {
      "start": 289.88,
      "end": 291.24,
      "text": "쓸 수가 있겠네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 291.24,
      "end": 292.78,
      "text": "That's what I'm thinking about right now"
    },
    {
      "start": 292.78,
      "end": 294.34,
      "text": "If I were her dad"
    },
    {
      "start": 294.34,
      "end": 295.88,
      "text": "What is the other option?"
    },
    {
      "start": 296.06,
      "end": 298.12,
      "text": "What should I do in this situation?"
    },
    {
      "start": 298.34,
      "end": 299.46,
      "text": "In his shoes?"
    },
    {
      "start": 301.22,
      "end": 302.94,
      "text": "Give a child up for adoption"
    },
    {
      "start": 302.94,
      "end": 304.94,
      "text": "Give a child up for adoption"
    },
    {
      "start": 304.94,
      "end": 307.4,
      "text": "아이를 입양 보내다"
    },
    {
      "start": 307.4,
      "end": 308.26,
      "text": "라는 표현입니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 308.26,
      "end": 310.14,
      "text": "A grace period"
    },
    {
      "start": 310.14,
      "end": 312.18,
      "text": "A grace period"
    },
    {
      "start": 312.18,
      "end": 313.66,
      "text": "라는 게 소위"
    },
    {
      "start": 313.66,
      "end": 315.14,
      "text": "유예 기간"
    },
    {
      "start": 315.14,
      "end": 316.54,
      "text": "이라는 명칭입니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 316.54,
      "end": 318.54,
      "text": "Yeah, this has to do with the adoption"
    },
    {
      "start": 318.54,
      "end": 319.12,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 319.12,
      "end": 320.48,
      "text": "There was a grace period"
    },
    {
      "start": 320.48,
      "end": 321.94,
      "text": "And that happens to be"
    },
    {
      "start": 321.94,
      "end": 323.26,
      "text": "his daughter's name"
    },
    {
      "start": 323.26,
      "end": 324.64,
      "text": "His daughter's name is Grace"
    },
    {
      "start": 324.64,
      "end": 326.8,
      "text": "이게 what a coincidence인지"
    },
    {
      "start": 326.8,
      "end": 327.7,
      "text": "아니면 뭔가"
    },
    {
      "start": 327.7,
      "end": 329.3,
      "text": "He had a grace period"
    },
    {
      "start": 329.3,
      "end": 330.86,
      "text": "for 30 days"
    },
    {
      "start": 330.86,
      "end": 331.72,
      "text": "as I remember"
    },
    {
      "start": 331.72,
      "end": 332.9,
      "text": "Yeah, after you decide"
    },
    {
      "start": 332.9,
      "end": 334.22,
      "text": "to give your kid up for adoption"
    },
    {
      "start": 334.22,
      "end": 335.9,
      "text": "you can change your mind"
    },
    {
      "start": 335.9,
      "end": 338.04,
      "text": "within 30 days"
    },
    {
      "start": 338.04,
      "end": 338.36,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 338.36,
      "end": 339.32,
      "text": "That's the grace period"
    },
    {
      "start": 339.32,
      "end": 341.04,
      "text": "그래서 he named his daughter"
    },
    {
      "start": 341.04,
      "end": 341.66,
      "text": "Grace?"
    },
    {
      "start": 342.22,
      "end": 342.72,
      "text": "Maybe"
    },
    {
      "start": 342.72,
      "end": 343.42,
      "text": "Maybe"
    },
    {
      "start": 343.42,
      "end": 344.84,
      "text": "It's a coincidence"
    },
    {
      "start": 344.84,
      "end": 345.06,
      "text": "I'm not sure"
    },
    {
      "start": 345.06,
      "end": 347.34,
      "text": "Anyway, it's a very fitting name"
    },
    {
      "start": 347.34,
      "end": 347.68,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 347.68,
      "end": 350.08,
      "text": "참 우연인지 아닌지는 모르겠지만"
    },
    {
      "start": 350.08,
      "end": 350.7,
      "text": "아무튼"
    },
    {
      "start": 350.7,
      "end": 351.82,
      "text": "a grace period"
    },
    {
      "start": 351.82,
      "end": 353.82,
      "text": "유예 기간이라는 의미였고"
    },
    {
      "start": 353.82,
      "end": 355.38,
      "text": "이 딸의 이름도"
    },
    {
      "start": 355.38,
      "end": 356.36,
      "text": "Grace였다"
    },
    {
      "start": 356.36,
      "end": 357.14,
      "text": "하는 것까지"
    },
    {
      "start": 357.14,
      "end": 357.94,
      "text": "알려드립니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 357.94,
      "end": 358.64,
      "text": "Perfect name"
    },
    {
      "start": 358.64,
      "end": 358.94,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 358.94,
      "end": 359.96,
      "text": "자, 이 장면"
    },
    {
      "start": 359.96,
      "end": 360.84,
      "text": "다시 한번 들어볼게요"
    },
    {
      "start": 360.84,
      "end": 362.96,
      "text": "I hate fighting with you"
    },
    {
      "start": 362.96,
      "end": 365.62,
      "text": "You think you're ever going to forgive me?"
    },
    {
      "start": 366.56,
      "end": 367.56,
      "text": "That's my other option"
    },
    {
      "start": 367.56,
      "end": 369.46,
      "text": "But I want to know everything"
    },
    {
      "start": 369.46,
      "end": 372.1,
      "text": "When you give a child up for adoption"
    },
    {
      "start": 372.1,
      "end": 373.73,
      "text": "you've got 30 days"
    },
    {
      "start": 373.73,
      "end": 374.53,
      "text": "to change your mind"
    },
    {
      "start": 374.53,
      "end": 376.63,
      "text": "A grace period"
    },
    {
      "start": 376.63,
      "end": 378.63,
      "text": "How long did it take you"
    },
    {
      "start": 378.63,
      "end": 379.59,
      "text": "to decide to come get me?"
    },
    {
      "start": 380.11,
      "end": 380.95,
      "text": "29 days"
    },
    {
      "start": 380.95,
      "end": 382.43,
      "text": "와우"
    },
    {
      "start": 382.43,
      "end": 384.27,
      "text": "29일간"
    },
    {
      "start": 384.27,
      "end": 386.23,
      "text": "얼마나 많은 고민과"
    },
    {
      "start": 386.23,
      "end": 387.77,
      "text": "갈등을 했을지"
    },
    {
      "start": 387.77,
      "end": 388.71,
      "text": "가슴이 굉장히"
    },
    {
      "start": 388.71,
      "end": 389.61,
      "text": "먹먹해졌어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 389.61,
      "end": 389.91,
      "text": "저는"
    },
    {
      "start": 389.91,
      "end": 390.75,
      "text": "Yeah, me too"
    },
    {
      "start": 390.75,
      "end": 393.21,
      "text": "He waited until the very last day"
    },
    {
      "start": 393.21,
      "end": 393.89,
      "text": "That's right"
    },
    {
      "start": 393.89,
      "end": 395.03,
      "text": "To take her back"
    },
    {
      "start": 395.03,
      "end": 396.23,
      "text": "and raise her"
    },
    {
      "start": 396.23,
      "end": 397.41,
      "text": "as his own daughter"
    },
    {
      "start": 397.41,
      "end": 399.83,
      "text": "자, Grace가 먼저"
    },
    {
      "start": 399.83,
      "end": 400.87,
      "text": "뭐라고 했죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 401.84,
      "end": 403.22,
      "text": "I hate fighting with you"
    },
    {
      "start": 403.22,
      "end": 405.18,
      "text": "아빠랑 싸우는 거"
    },
    {
      "start": 405.18,
      "end": 405.66,
      "text": "hate"
    },
    {
      "start": 405.66,
      "end": 406.32,
      "text": "싫어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 406.32,
      "end": 407.74,
      "text": "I hate fighting with you"
    },
    {
      "start": 407.74,
      "end": 408.82,
      "text": "Oh, I would feel so good"
    },
    {
      "start": 408.82,
      "end": 409.6,
      "text": "as a dad"
    },
    {
      "start": 409.6,
      "end": 411.52,
      "text": "when she comes up to me"
    },
    {
      "start": 411.52,
      "end": 412.52,
      "text": "after fighting"
    },
    {
      "start": 412.52,
      "end": 414.18,
      "text": "I hate fighting with you, dad"
    },
    {
      "start": 414.18,
      "end": 416.06,
      "text": "Oh, 딸이 아빠한테"
    },
    {
      "start": 416.06,
      "end": 418.14,
      "text": "아빠, 나는 아빠랑 싸우는 거 싫어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 418.14,
      "end": 418.9,
      "text": "이렇게 이야기를 하면"
    },
    {
      "start": 418.9,
      "end": 420.5,
      "text": "얼마나 더 사랑스러워 보일까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 420.9,
      "end": 422.02,
      "text": "Let's make up"
    },
    {
      "start": 422.02,
      "end": 423.48,
      "text": "우리 화해해요"
    },
    {
      "start": 423.48,
      "end": 425.02,
      "text": "If it's your wife or husband"
    },
    {
      "start": 425.02,
      "end": 426.44,
      "text": "그냥 가만히 있어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 426.44,
      "end": 427.62,
      "text": "그냥 가만히 있어요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 428.44,
      "end": 430.02,
      "text": "It's not so amazing"
    },
    {
      "start": 430.02,
      "end": 430.9,
      "text": "아, 그래요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 431.08,
      "end": 432.7,
      "text": "역시 딸과 다르네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 432.7,
      "end": 433.5,
      "text": "존재 자체가"
    },
    {
      "start": 433.5,
      "end": 434.78,
      "text": "물론 양적 좋지만"
    },
    {
      "start": 434.78,
      "end": 436.44,
      "text": "딸 더 달라요"
    },
    {
      "start": 436.44,
      "end": 438.18,
      "text": "그래서 피는 물보다 진하다라는"
    },
    {
      "start": 438.18,
      "end": 439.62,
      "text": "속담이 딱이네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 439.62,
      "end": 440.08,
      "text": "Yes"
    },
    {
      "start": 440.08,
      "end": 441.66,
      "text": "Especially father, daughter"
    },
    {
      "start": 441.66,
      "end": 442.62,
      "text": "mother, daughter"
    },
    {
      "start": 442.62,
      "end": 444.58,
      "text": "부모, 자식"
    },
    {
      "start": 444.58,
      "end": 445.2,
      "text": "그 피"
    },
    {
      "start": 445.2,
      "end": 445.64,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 445.64,
      "end": 446.16,
      "text": "그 피"
    },
    {
      "start": 446.16,
      "end": 447.36,
      "text": "is very, very 진해"
    },
    {
      "start": 447.36,
      "end": 447.66,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 447.66,
      "end": 450.52,
      "text": "You think you're ever gonna forgive me?"
    },
    {
      "start": 451.02,
      "end": 452.58,
      "text": "아빠가 이렇게 대답했습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 452.58,
      "end": 454.9,
      "text": "You think you're ever gonna forgive me?"
    },
    {
      "start": 455.62,
      "end": 458.22,
      "text": "나를 용서할 수 있겠니?"
    },
    {
      "start": 458.48,
      "end": 459.0,
      "text": "라는 겁니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 459.0,
      "end": 460.96,
      "text": "What's my other option?"
    },
    {
      "start": 461.76,
      "end": 463.26,
      "text": "뭐, 또 다른 선택지가 있어요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 463.52,
      "end": 464.6,
      "text": "라는 질문이잖아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 464.6,
      "end": 466.92,
      "text": "뭐, 화해할 수밖에 없잖아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 466.92,
      "end": 468.0,
      "text": "라는 뉘앙스입니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 468.0,
      "end": 469.22,
      "text": "What's my other option?"
    },
    {
      "start": 469.7,
      "end": 470.62,
      "text": "That's good"
    },
    {
      "start": 470.62,
      "end": 472.36,
      "text": "She can't just leave her dad"
    },
    {
      "start": 472.36,
      "end": 473.97,
      "text": "But"
    },
    {
      "start": 473.97,
      "end": 475.65,
      "text": "Oh, condition-y so"
    },
    {
      "start": 475.65,
      "end": 475.97,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 475.97,
      "end": 476.85,
      "text": "I have a condition"
    },
    {
      "start": 476.85,
      "end": 477.15,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 477.15,
      "end": 479.31,
      "text": "I wanna know everything"
    },
    {
      "start": 479.31,
      "end": 480.63,
      "text": "화해를 할 테니"
    },
    {
      "start": 480.63,
      "end": 482.55,
      "text": "조건을 이야기하는 거네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 482.55,
      "end": 484.15,
      "text": "But I wanna know everything"
    },
    {
      "start": 484.15,
      "end": 486.07,
      "text": "하지만 대신에"
    },
    {
      "start": 486.07,
      "end": 488.05,
      "text": "나는 모든 거를 다 알기를 원해요"
    },
    {
      "start": 488.05,
      "end": 488.73,
      "text": "라는 거니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 488.73,
      "end": 490.53,
      "text": "That's a very understandable condition"
    },
    {
      "start": 490.53,
      "end": 490.95,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 490.95,
      "end": 493.33,
      "text": "솔직하게 모든 일을 다 말해주세요"
    },
    {
      "start": 493.33,
      "end": 494.31,
      "text": "라는 의미가 되겠죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 494.31,
      "end": 495.69,
      "text": "Okay, now her dad"
    },
    {
      "start": 495.69,
      "end": 497.07,
      "text": "is gonna tell her everything"
    },
    {
      "start": 497.07,
      "end": 499.97,
      "text": "When you give a child up for adoption"
    },
    {
      "start": 499.97,
      "end": 501.71,
      "text": "you've got 30 days"
    },
    {
      "start": 501.71,
      "end": 502.79,
      "text": "to change your mind"
    },
    {
      "start": 502.79,
      "end": 505.77,
      "text": "When you give a child up for adoption"
    },
    {
      "start": 505.77,
      "end": 508.39,
      "text": "아이를 입양 보낼 때"
    },
    {
      "start": 508.39,
      "end": 510.63,
      "text": "you've got 30 days"
    },
    {
      "start": 510.63,
      "end": 512.39,
      "text": "to change your mind"
    },
    {
      "start": 512.39,
      "end": 513.13,
      "text": "라고 했습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 513.13,
      "end": 515.95,
      "text": "너의 마음을 바꿀 수 있는"
    },
    {
      "start": 515.95,
      "end": 517.97,
      "text": "30일이 주어진다"
    },
    {
      "start": 517.97,
      "end": 518.41,
      "text": "라는 거예요"
    },
    {
      "start": 518.41,
      "end": 520.27,
      "text": "30일 안에 마음을 바꿀 수 있어"
    },
    {
      "start": 520.27,
      "end": 521.45,
      "text": "I didn't know this"
    },
    {
      "start": 521.45,
      "end": 522.23,
      "text": "Me neither"
    },
    {
      "start": 522.23,
      "end": 523.13,
      "text": "But this makes sense"
    },
    {
      "start": 523.13,
      "end": 523.61,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 523.61,
      "end": 525.09,
      "text": "It's a big decision"
    },
    {
      "start": 525.09,
      "end": 527.01,
      "text": "되게 좋은 기간인 것 같아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 527.01,
      "end": 527.57,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 527.57,
      "end": 528.77,
      "text": "So I guess they keep the baby"
    },
    {
      "start": 528.77,
      "end": 529.45,
      "text": "in a hospital"
    },
    {
      "start": 529.45,
      "end": 530.65,
      "text": "or orphanage"
    },
    {
      "start": 530.65,
      "end": 531.71,
      "text": "for 30 days"
    },
    {
      "start": 531.71,
      "end": 533.41,
      "text": "until they decide"
    },
    {
      "start": 533.41,
      "end": 534.99,
      "text": "make the final decision"
    },
    {
      "start": 534.99,
      "end": 537.33,
      "text": "A grace period"
    },
    {
      "start": 537.33,
      "end": 537.99,
      "text": "바로 그게"
    },
    {
      "start": 537.99,
      "end": 539.27,
      "text": "A grace period"
    },
    {
      "start": 539.27,
      "end": 540.47,
      "text": "라는 거라는 겁니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 540.47,
      "end": 542.15,
      "text": "유예 기간이지"
    },
    {
      "start": 542.15,
      "end": 542.91,
      "text": "라고 하면서"
    },
    {
      "start": 542.91,
      "end": 544.07,
      "text": "이 아빠가요"
    },
    {
      "start": 544.07,
      "end": 545.69,
      "text": "목소리가 울먹 울먹 했어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 545.69,
      "end": 547.13,
      "text": "특히 period"
    },
    {
      "start": 547.13,
      "end": 548.13,
      "text": "라고 이야기할 때"
    },
    {
      "start": 548.13,
      "end": 549.13,
      "text": "She's a grace"
    },
    {
      "start": 549.13,
      "end": 550.53,
      "text": "and he starts crying"
    },
    {
      "start": 550.53,
      "end": 551.37,
      "text": "period"
    },
    {
      "start": 551.37,
      "end": 552.07,
      "text": "그쵸"
    },
    {
      "start": 552.07,
      "end": 552.93,
      "text": "A grace period"
    },
    {
      "start": 552.93,
      "end": 553.21,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 553.21,
      "end": 554.53,
      "text": "You can feel his emotion"
    },
    {
      "start": 554.53,
      "end": 557.36,
      "text": "How long did it take you"
    },
    {
      "start": 557.36,
      "end": 558.96,
      "text": "to decide to come get me?"
    },
    {
      "start": 559.38,
      "end": 561.08,
      "text": "아주 똑똑하게 질문을 하네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 561.08,
      "end": 561.84,
      "text": "Very idiot"
    },
    {
      "start": 561.84,
      "end": 563.62,
      "text": "Very good question"
    },
    {
      "start": 563.62,
      "end": 566.02,
      "text": "How long did it take you"
    },
    {
      "start": 566.02,
      "end": 566.88,
      "text": "to decide"
    },
    {
      "start": 566.88,
      "end": 568.32,
      "text": "to come get me?"
    },
    {
      "start": 568.42,
      "end": 568.88,
      "text": "라고 했습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 568.88,
      "end": 570.02,
      "text": "잘 들리셨죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 570.52,
      "end": 572.04,
      "text": "얼마나 오래 걸렸어요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 572.04,
      "end": 573.38,
      "text": "결정하는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 573.38,
      "end": 575.48,
      "text": "나를 데리러 오려고"
    },
    {
      "start": 575.48,
      "end": 576.12,
      "text": "결정하는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 576.12,
      "end": 577.5,
      "text": "얼마나 오래 걸렸어요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 577.7,
      "end": 578.2,
      "text": "라는 겁니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 578.2,
      "end": 578.94,
      "text": "What did you think"
    },
    {
      "start": 578.94,
      "end": 579.68,
      "text": "he was going to say?"
    },
    {
      "start": 579.76,
      "end": 581.1,
      "text": "I thought he was going to say"
    },
    {
      "start": 581.1,
      "end": 582.6,
      "text": "like one hour"
    },
    {
      "start": 582.6,
      "end": 583.76,
      "text": "I went right back"
    },
    {
      "start": 583.76,
      "end": 584.36,
      "text": "Right away"
    },
    {
      "start": 584.36,
      "end": 584.96,
      "text": "Right away"
    },
    {
      "start": 584.96,
      "end": 585.86,
      "text": "to get you"
    },
    {
      "start": 585.86,
      "end": 586.74,
      "text": "because you're my daughter"
    },
    {
      "start": 586.74,
      "end": 587.1,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 587.1,
      "end": 588.26,
      "text": "And I didn't want to give you"
    },
    {
      "start": 588.26,
      "end": 588.92,
      "text": "up for adoption"
    },
    {
      "start": 588.92,
      "end": 590.08,
      "text": "오, 그럴 줄 알았는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 590.08,
      "end": 591.3,
      "text": "대답은?"
    },
    {
      "start": 591.7,
      "end": 592.74,
      "text": "29 days"
    },
    {
      "start": 592.74,
      "end": 593.28,
      "text": "이거였습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 593.28,
      "end": 594.34,
      "text": "29 days"
    },
    {
      "start": 594.34,
      "end": 595.1,
      "text": "오, surprise"
    },
    {
      "start": 595.1,
      "end": 596.5,
      "text": "오, 그러니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 596.5,
      "end": 598.14,
      "text": "왠지 좀 더 신중하고"
    },
    {
      "start": 598.14,
      "end": 598.92,
      "text": "또 신중하고"
    },
    {
      "start": 598.92,
      "end": 600.18,
      "text": "또 신중하기 위해서"
    },
    {
      "start": 600.18,
      "end": 601.64,
      "text": "이마만큼의 기간을"
    },
    {
      "start": 601.64,
      "end": 602.42,
      "text": "끈 게 아닌가"
    },
    {
      "start": 602.42,
      "end": 603.04,
      "text": "싶어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 603.04,
      "end": 604.86,
      "text": "Maybe her mom"
    },
    {
      "start": 604.86,
      "end": 605.76,
      "text": "was already gone"
    },
    {
      "start": 605.76,
      "end": 607.58,
      "text": "so he was really worried"
    },
    {
      "start": 607.58,
      "end": 608.8,
      "text": "Can I raise this girl"
    },
    {
      "start": 608.8,
      "end": 609.5,
      "text": "by myself?"
    },
    {
      "start": 609.62,
      "end": 610.14,
      "text": "맞아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 610.14,
      "end": 611.44,
      "text": "He waited 29 days"
    },
    {
      "start": 611.44,
      "end": 612.96,
      "text": "29일 만에"
    },
    {
      "start": 612.96,
      "end": 613.8,
      "text": "그래도 다행히"
    },
    {
      "start": 613.8,
      "end": 615.06,
      "text": "그레이스를 찾아왔네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 615.06,
      "end": 616.04,
      "text": "네, 마지막으로"
    },
    {
      "start": 616.04,
      "end": 617.02,
      "text": "한 번 더 들어보겠습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 617.02,
      "end": 618.9,
      "text": "I hate fighting with you"
    },
    {
      "start": 618.9,
      "end": 620.48,
      "text": "You think you're ever"
    },
    {
      "start": 620.48,
      "end": 621.58,
      "text": "going to forgive me?"
    },
    {
      "start": 622.5,
      "end": 623.52,
      "text": "That's my other option"
    },
    {
      "start": 623.52,
      "end": 625.44,
      "text": "But I want to know everything"
    },
    {
      "start": 625.44,
      "end": 627.43,
      "text": "When you give a child"
    },
    {
      "start": 627.43,
      "end": 628.07,
      "text": "up for adoption"
    },
    {
      "start": 628.07,
      "end": 629.69,
      "text": "you've got 30 days"
    },
    {
      "start": 629.69,
      "end": 630.47,
      "text": "to change your mind"
    },
    {
      "start": 630.47,
      "end": 632.59,
      "text": "A grace period"
    },
    {
      "start": 632.59,
      "end": 633.88,
      "text": "How long did it"
    },
    {
      "start": 633.88,
      "end": 634.96,
      "text": "take you to decide"
    },
    {
      "start": 634.96,
      "end": 635.56,
      "text": "to come get me?"
    },
    {
      "start": 636.1,
      "end": 636.88,
      "text": "29 days"
    },
    {
      "start": 636.88,
      "end": 639.85,
      "text": "I like this conversation"
    },
    {
      "start": 639.85,
      "end": 642.03,
      "text": "It was a sincere conversation"
    },
    {
      "start": 642.03,
      "end": 642.77,
      "text": "Very sincere"
    },
    {
      "start": 642.77,
      "end": 643.41,
      "text": "Honest"
    },
    {
      "start": 643.41,
      "end": 644.81,
      "text": "It's a conversation"
    },
    {
      "start": 644.81,
      "end": 645.81,
      "text": "they needed to have"
    },
    {
      "start": 645.81,
      "end": 647.15,
      "text": "a little earlier in life"
    },
    {
      "start": 647.15,
      "end": 647.63,
      "text": "That's right"
    },
    {
      "start": 647.63,
      "end": 648.91,
      "text": "그랬으면 좋았을 텐데"
    },
    {
      "start": 648.91,
      "end": 650.35,
      "text": "At least they're having it now"
    },
    {
      "start": 650.35,
      "end": 651.57,
      "text": "맞아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 651.57,
      "end": 652.75,
      "text": "지금이"
    },
    {
      "start": 652.75,
      "end": 653.77,
      "text": "그래도"
    },
    {
      "start": 653.77,
      "end": 654.65,
      "text": "주어졌을 때"
    },
    {
      "start": 654.65,
      "end": 655.75,
      "text": "시간이 주어졌을 때"
    },
    {
      "start": 655.75,
      "end": 656.79,
      "text": "이야기를 해주면"
    },
    {
      "start": 656.79,
      "end": 657.85,
      "text": "이렇게 오해가 풀립니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 657.85,
      "end": 660.77,
      "text": "네, 오늘 스크린 잉글리쉬는 여기까지고요"
    },
    {
      "start": 660.77,
      "end": 662.69,
      "text": "크리스는 내일 다시 만날게요"
    },
    {
      "start": 662.69,
      "end": 663.43,
      "text": "See you tomorrow"
    }
  ]
}